Package com.hp.opencall.jmsc.test Description

Root package for the JSR 309 testcases.
On top of some utility classes used throughout the suite, here reside a test class "SimplePlayTest" that browses gradually the necessary steps to play a file to a caller. This test class is handy to determine if the media server is operational.
